> **This is similar to how SQLite, Qt (LGPL with exceptions), or the Unreal Engine's EULA operate** – you can ship the compiled code inside your product, but you may not redistribute the source as a standalone SDK.

> **Free for all uses** – startups, enterprises, research, side projects, and commercial products.
